127
00:13:00,870 --> 00:13:02,940
- This...
- Quickly go out.

128
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:05,210
Yes.

129
00:13:07,940 --> 00:13:10,010
Third Uncle...

130
00:13:10,010 --> 00:13:13,300
What went wrong? Where's Su Su?

131
00:13:13,300 --> 00:13:15,440
Ye Hua, listen to me.

132
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:19,050
After you got hacked by the Merpeople Chieftain three days ago,

133
00:13:19,050 --> 00:13:23,400
that mortal wife of yours went beyond the barrier you set up.

134
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:28,450
What did you say? Why?

135
00:13:28,450 --> 00:13:33,540
She stepped out of your barrier and was discovered by Father Monarch.

136
00:13:33,540 --> 00:13:37,050
Heavenly Monarch...

137
00:13:37,050 --> 00:13:39,830
Ye Hua!

138
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:44,500
- Let go of me! Let go...
- Ye Hua, listen to me!

139
00:13:44,500 --> 00:13:49,380
