146
00:14:29,020 --> 00:14:34,150
After you recuperate for a few days, we'll return to the Heavenly Palace.

147
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:35,530
No.

148
00:14:36,540 --> 00:14:38,800
We mustn't rush to return.

149
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:41,230
