156
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:32,950
His Third Highness was afraid that this matter might affect the battle, so he suppressed it first.

157
00:15:32,950 --> 00:15:34,970
How is the Crown Prince now?

158
00:15:34,970 --> 00:15:40,800
Based on the assessment of Medicine King, His Highness the Crown Prince was able to preserve his spirit.

159
00:15:44,680 --> 00:15:46,350
That's good.

160
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:51,240
You've always followed the Crown Prince,

161
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:55,330
yet you let him be in such danger and he almost died because of it.

162
00:15:57,960 --> 00:16:03,610
Once the main army returns, go to Lord of Puhua to seek punishment.

163
00:16:03,610 --> 00:16:04,990
Yes.

164
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,470
Wait!

165
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:09,940
Heavenly Monarch.

166
00:16:11,520 --> 00:16:14,600
The invitation for the religious assembly of Lord of Lingbao has been distributed.

167
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:18,890
Immortals from all over the Four Seas and Eight Wildernesses will be coming here.

168
00:16:18,890 --> 00:16:22,070
I can only go to Long Sea after that.

169
00:16:22,070 --> 00:16:25,700
Tell His Highness the Third Prince to take good care of him.

170
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:27,970
Yes.

171
00:16:38,590 --> 00:16:42,670
Your Highness, we really have to see His Mighty Monarch.

172
00:16:42,670 --> 00:16:46,600
Even if the sky falls down now, His Mighty Monarch won't be coming here.

173
00:16:46,640 --> 00:16:50,080
Your Highness, the Crown Prince of the Heavenly Tribe almost died in the hands of the Merpeople Tribe.

174
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:52,550
The Merpeople Tribe are, after all, a sub-branch of ours.

175
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:56,700
If the Heavenly Tribe blames us, our Winged Tribe will be in trouble again.

176
00:16:57,730 --> 00:17:04,120
Even when Qing Cang was sealed, our Winged Tribe didn't get in trouble. It will also be the same now.

177
00:17:04,120 --> 00:17:08,060
Unruly! How dare you directly mention the name of the Winged Monarch?!

178
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:11,910
You're the bold one.

179
00:17:11,910 --> 00:17:16,870
Could it be that after 70,000 years, you only obey Qing Cang, and not His Mighty Monarch?

180
00:17:16,870 --> 00:17:21,560
Winged Monarch? Who's the real ruler of this Grand Purple Palace?!

181
00:17:21,560 --> 00:17:23,510
