192
00:18:27,190 --> 00:18:29,180
I had no choice, either.

193
00:18:29,180 --> 00:18:34,690
So I use delivering the invitation as a pretext to ask you when you plan to return to the Winged Realm.

194
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:37,810
I will go directly to the Heavenly Palace.

195
00:18:43,930 --> 00:18:49,000
Your Mighty Monarch, are you going to the religious assembly to lecture and discuss religious laws?

196
00:18:50,800 --> 00:18:53,150
Since when have I known how to lecture?

197
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:56,450
What will I know how to discuss?

198
00:18:57,580 --> 00:19:03,260
I'm merely admitting my mistake and offering a humble apology to the Heavenly Tribe.

199
00:19:06,990 --> 00:19:13,100
Regardless of whatever reasons you give, privately taking my commander's seal is a major sin.

200
00:19:16,780 --> 00:19:22,500
Since we are a married couple, I won't punish you for your sin.

201
00:19:23,550 --> 00:19:26,090
Return to the palace and reflect upon yourself.

202
00:19:27,330 --> 00:19:32,090
Your Mighty Monarch, you can't do this to me.

203
00:19:32,580 --> 00:19:38,030
My womb is pregnant with your child.

204
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:43,770
