213
00:20:35,650 --> 00:20:38,240
I will go back to the palace with you.

214
00:21:05,180 --> 00:21:07,210
Medicine King, quick!

215
00:21:07,210 --> 00:21:12,480
- This... What's going on?
- Save him now.

216
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:15,790
Your Highness, Your Highness.

217
00:21:24,350 --> 00:21:26,150
