253
00:24:46,680 --> 00:24:49,250
You don't know, either.

254
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:56,850
Ye Hua.

255
00:24:58,100 --> 00:25:02,260
Hey, wait. I still have something to ask you.

256
00:25:03,810 --> 00:25:05,410
Don't cry yet.

257
00:25:05,410 --> 00:25:08,360
Wait! Wait!

258
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:20,510
Heavenly Monarch doesn't want us to talk to the mortal, nor let anyone know about this.

259
00:25:20,510 --> 00:25:23,820
Could it be that while His Highness the Crown Prince, isn't around, this mortal will be—

260
00:25:23,820 --> 00:25:25,960
It's unspeakable. It's unspeakable.

261
00:25:25,960 --> 00:25:28,790
Did you forget about the incident regarding the Water Monarch of Northern Sea?

262
00:25:39,900 --> 00:25:45,800
I should feel angry on behalf of my aunt, but why do I feel a bit sad?

263
00:25:48,380 --> 00:25:52,070
Frankly, this mortal is rather pitiful.

264
00:25:53,300 --> 00:25:55,300
I'm not eating. I'm not eating.

265
00:25:55,300 --> 00:25:57,610
I want to look for Ye Hua.

266
00:26:10,060 --> 00:26:13,660
Your Mighty Monarch, do you really want to go to Heavenly Palace?

267
00:26:15,150 --> 00:26:17,670
The Merpeople Tribe is a sub-tribe of the Winged Tribe.

268
00:26:17,670 --> 00:26:20,240
Although they broke away from us for 70,000 years,

269
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:23,190
they injured the Crown Prince of the Heavenly Tribe this time.

270
00:26:23,890 --> 00:26:26,210
I can't be absolved from the blame.

271
00:26:27,850 --> 00:26:33,580
I'm taking advantage of the religious ceremony of Lord of Lingbao to go to Heavenly Palace and apologize.

272
00:26:33,580 --> 00:26:36,030
Lest the Winged Tribe is implicated.

273
00:26:36,030 --> 00:26:37,590
I understand.

274
00:26:37,590 --> 00:26:41,060
You are doing this for the Winged Tribe,

275
00:26:41,060 --> 00:26:46,560
but for this 70,000 years, these three days are the happiest I've been.

276
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:49,040
I can't bear to see you leave.

277
00:26:51,750 --> 00:26:53,950
Take care of your health.

278
00:26:53,950 --> 00:26:59,220
Shaman, why is the Monarchess feeling uncomfortable right after becoming pregnant?

279
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:11,990
The Winged Monarchess is an immortal carrying a child from the Winged Tribe,

280
00:27:11,990 --> 00:27:14,430
so it's unavoidable their qi would contradict each other.

281
00:27:14,430 --> 00:27:17,200
I think she should lie in bed more often.

282
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:20,960
When it's a few months older, she will naturally feel better.

283
00:27:21,420 --> 00:27:23,120
That's good then.

284
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:26,040
Let the shaman stay here and keep you company then.

285
00:27:29,690 --> 00:27:33,670
No. Ever since you took over the throne, you have never gone to Heavenly Palace.

286
00:27:33,670 --> 00:27:39,300
Since you are going to the religious ceremony, as the monarchess of the Winged Tribe, I should be with you.

287
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:41,270
You are pregnant with a Winged Tribe child.

288
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:43,460
That's contradictory to your immortal qi to begin with.

289
00:27:43,460 --> 00:27:47,560
If you go to Heavenly Palace, your health won't be able to take it.

290
00:27:47,950 --> 00:27:49,630
It's not a problem for me.

291
00:27:49,630 --> 00:27:53,770
When mortal women are pregnant, they sometimes will feel uncomfortable, too.

292
00:27:53,770 --> 00:27:57,620
I'm the monarchess of the Winged Tribe. How could I be so delicate?

293
00:28:01,500 --> 00:28:03,000
Okay.

294
00:29:25,700 --> 00:29:29,200
During the 49 days of the ceremony, Winged Monarch, you will be staying here.

295
00:29:29,200 --> 00:29:32,000
If you need anything, please tell me.

296
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:33,700
Thank you, Immortal.

297
00:29:40,800 --> 00:29:43,300
Then, I'll take my leave.

298
00:29:43,300 --> 00:29:45,400
May I ask?

299
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:50,800
Do you know where the Cold Moon Lotus gifted from the Winged Realm 70,000 years ago is kept?

300
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:55,000
Cold Moon Lotus? It's in the lotus pond next to Zhaohua Palace.

301
00:29:56,500 --> 00:29:58,200
Can you take me there and see?

302
00:29:58,200 --> 00:29:59,800
Yes.

303
00:30:01,540 --> 00:30:03,280
I'll be back soon.

304
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:07,400
I'm feeling a bit...

305
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:11,400
I don't feel too well, so I won't accompany you there.

306
00:30:13,130 --> 00:30:15,550
- Stay here and keep her company.
- Yes.

307
00:30:46,200 --> 00:30:49,200
Didn't you say you would surely help me to keep this child?

308
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:51,600
Why am I always in pain?

309
00:30:51,600 --> 00:30:55,000
It could be that for the past few years, since you are an immortal,

310
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:59,500
living in the Winged Realm for too long has ruined your health.

311
00:30:59,500 --> 00:31:03,000
You're not quite suitable for having a child anymore.

312
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:04,800
Not suitable?

313
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:07,400
Then, what am I carrying right now?

314
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:09,300
Your Highness, I...

315
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:15,800
I already cannot feel the little prince's pulse.

316
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:20,400
What did you say?!

317
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:22,650
Your Highness, calm down.

318
00:31:22,650 --> 00:31:24,800
Everything I've said is true.

319
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:28,200
The little prince does not have any signs of life.

320
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:30,600
In my opinion, you should go back to the Winged Realm.

321
00:31:30,600 --> 00:31:34,800
I will prescribe some medicine to make the little prince...

322
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:37,400
Your Highness, it's already at this stage.

323
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:41,000
Your body is more important.

324
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:45,400
No, I need to keep this child.

325
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:47,600
Don't you see?

326
00:31:47,600 --> 00:31:51,600
For 70,000 years, His Mighty Monarch has never been this patient with me.

327
00:31:53,600 --> 00:31:55,780
I need to keep this child.

328
00:31:55,780 --> 00:31:57,600
I need to!

329
00:32:02,300 --> 00:32:05,100
Don't tell anyone. Do you hear me?

330
00:32:05,100 --> 00:32:07,400
Or else I will kill you!

331
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:09,800
I will take the lives of your entire clan!

332
00:32:09,800 --> 00:32:13,200
I will keep my mouth shut.

333
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:23,210
Where's the peach blossom scent coming from?

334
00:32:23,210 --> 00:32:25,000
It's so familiar.

335
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:27,000
[Zhaohua Palace]

336
00:33:01,800 --> 00:33:03,500
Winged Monarch.

337
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:09,900
Lord of Lingbao.

338
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:17,800
We haven't seen each other for many thousand years.

339
00:33:17,800 --> 00:33:21,300
I almost couldn't recognize you from the back.

340
00:33:22,700 --> 00:33:26,200
Yes, it's been 70,000 years.

341
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:31,900
I remember that the first time we met was at Kunlun Void.

342
00:33:33,500 --> 00:33:38,400
I heard from the divine maids that you just arrived here.

343
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:43,100
How did you find the mood and leisure to enjoy the lotuses here?

344
00:33:43,100 --> 00:33:45,700
I came to see the Cold Moon Lotus.

345
00:33:45,700 --> 00:33:50,600
I fear that since they lived in the Winged Realm for too long, they'd not be used to the lotus pond in the Heavenly Palace.

346
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:57,800
I didn't know you were so sensitive and caring.

347
00:33:57,800 --> 00:34:01,400
You care a lot about these lotus flowers.

348
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:07,800
- There's a fire! Extinguish the fire!
- Extinguish the fire!

349
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:10,600
- Someone help! 
- Zhaohua Palace?

350
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:15,400
Get them to put out the fire! There's someone locked up in there!

351
00:34:19,600 --> 00:34:21,500
How come there's a fire?

352
00:34:27,890 --> 00:34:29,660
It was my mount who set the fire.

353
00:34:29,660 --> 00:34:32,170
Please forgive me.

354
00:34:32,170 --> 00:34:34,910
Winged Monarch, don't blame yourself.

355
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:13,600
- Does she have any serious injuries?
- I'm not too sure.

356
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:17,400
I'll take her back to High Clear Plane for my shaman to take a look at her.

357
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:34,400
Ah Yin.

358
00:35:37,700 --> 00:35:39,500
Ah Yin.

359
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:46,600
How come she's here?

360
00:35:46,600 --> 00:35:49,600
No, it can't be.

361
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:55,400
Your Mighty Monarch, she must be an illusion from the Heavenly Tribe. This must be it.

362
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:58,000
They knew you have a personal friendship with High Immortal Si Yin,

363
00:35:58,000 --> 00:36:01,600
and they created an illusion of Si Yin to trick you.

364
00:36:01,600 --> 00:36:03,400
Shaman!

365
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:05,800
- Your Mighty Monarch.
- Quick.

366
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:09,800
Treat her injury now. She was hurt by the Red Lotus Fire. Hurry up.

367
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:11,500
Yes.

368
00:36:21,600 --> 00:36:23,700
How is she?

369
00:36:23,700 --> 00:36:27,600
Although she's an immortal, it's still problematic to be hit by the Red Lotus Fire.

370
00:36:27,600 --> 00:36:29,600
Check if...

371
00:36:30,310 --> 00:36:33,380
Your Mighty Monarch, she's just a mortal.

372
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:36,800
What? Mortal?

373
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:38,400
Mortal?

374
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:42,210
Yes, Your Mighty Monarch. She's not a high immortal.

375
00:36:42,210 --> 00:36:44,800
She's just a mortal woman.

376
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:48,000
- Are you sure?
- Yes.

377
00:36:57,100 --> 00:36:59,210
She doesn't have a divine aura.

378
00:36:59,210 --> 00:37:01,500
She's definitely a mortal.

379
00:37:03,600 --> 00:37:05,600
I was confused.

380
00:37:05,600 --> 00:37:08,900
I couldn't even differentiate between an immortal and mortal.

381
00:37:10,870 --> 00:37:13,680
- Treat her injury.
- Yes.

382
00:37:22,170 --> 00:37:27,250
If we were to say that this face resembles Si Yin, why not say that she looks more like Bai Qian?

383
00:37:27,250 --> 00:37:30,800
Fortunately, she's neither.

384
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:44,630
Come in.

385
00:37:48,790 --> 00:37:50,740
Your Mighty Monarch, I was wrong.

386
00:37:50,740 --> 00:37:53,410
You should know that this is not Grand Purple Palace in Winged Realm.

387
00:37:53,410 --> 00:37:55,510
This is Nine Heavens.

388
00:37:55,510 --> 00:37:58,250
Why did you use the Red Lotus Fire here?

389
00:37:58,250 --> 00:38:04,880
When I passed by the door of the deserted palace, I detected a familiar scent and went to find it.

390
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:10,020
Then, I saw this woman locked up in there and she was crying.

391
00:38:10,020 --> 00:38:14,470
Hence... I wanted to rescue her,

392
00:38:14,470 --> 00:38:17,370
but the lock on the door was made of millennium iron.

393
00:38:17,370 --> 00:38:19,770
I couldn't use magic to break it.

394
00:38:19,770 --> 00:38:22,400
Hence, you used fire to burn it?

395
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:27,490
Your Mighty Monarch, didn't you say that my Red Lotus Fire can burn anything?

396
00:38:29,110 --> 00:38:32,660
That's right. It can burn anything.

397
00:38:32,660 --> 00:38:35,850
That's why you can't control the power of the fire.

398
00:38:35,850 --> 00:38:37,700
You wanted to use fire to burn the lock.

399
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:39,700
Naturally, you would burn the bedroom.

400
00:38:39,700 --> 00:38:41,180
Forget it.

401
00:38:41,180 --> 00:38:45,050
I just hope Heavenly Monarch will not pursue this.

402
00:38:55,230 --> 00:38:57,200
Where's Ye Hua?

403
00:38:58,150 --> 00:39:01,460
- Where am I?
- Miss, do you feel better?

404
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:04,360
Who are you?

405
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:06,050
I'm the Winged Monarch, Li Jing.

406
00:39:06,050 --> 00:39:09,390
My mount made a mistake to set a fire just now.

407
00:39:09,390 --> 00:39:10,960
I'm very sorry.

408
00:39:10,960 --> 00:39:13,490
So, the fire was from you.

409
00:39:13,490 --> 00:39:16,980
I thought they wanted to kill me.

410
00:39:16,980 --> 00:39:18,850
They?

411
00:39:30,260 --> 00:39:32,120
How old are you?

412
00:39:32,120 --> 00:39:34,640
70,300 years old.

413
00:39:35,940 --> 00:39:38,800
70,300 years?

414
00:39:39,450 --> 00:39:43,250
Older Sister, the scent of peach blossom on your body smells very nice.

415
00:39:48,670 --> 00:39:52,340
You are a mortal. Why are you living in Heavenly Palace?

416
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:55,450
I was captured by them.

417
00:39:56,920 --> 00:39:59,280
Have you seen Ye Hua?

418
00:39:59,280 --> 00:40:02,090
Where is he now? How is he now?

419
00:40:02,090 --> 00:40:03,730
Ye Hua?

420
00:40:03,730 --> 00:40:05,950
Who are you to the Crown Prince?

421
00:40:18,770 --> 00:40:22,980
I'm the Crown Prince's, Ye Hua's, mother, Princess Consort Le Xu.

422
00:40:23,990 --> 00:40:25,960
Greetings, Your Highness Le Xu.

423
00:40:26,560 --> 00:40:28,830
Winged Monarch, no need to stand on ceremony.

424
00:40:28,830 --> 00:40:32,240
I heard you saved someone who belongs to me.

425
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:38,090
I specially came here to thank you and also, to take her back from you.

426
00:40:40,190 --> 00:40:42,680
She's from your palace?

427
00:40:42,680 --> 00:40:44,290
That's right.

428
00:40:44,290 --> 00:40:46,580
This woman broke the rules of Heaven.

429
00:40:46,580 --> 00:40:49,930
I originally locked her up in Zhaohua Palace to reflect.

430
00:40:49,930 --> 00:40:54,060
I didn't expect her to encounter a fire and was rescued by you.

431
00:40:55,130 --> 00:40:57,680
Go now and take her away.

432
00:40:57,680 --> 00:40:59,330
Yes.

433
00:41:12,180 --> 00:41:14,830
I will take my leave.

434
00:41:15,660 --> 00:41:17,580
Your Highness, take care.

435
00:41:36,880 --> 00:41:41,750
Your Majesty, that woman is pregnant. I fear...

436
00:41:41,750 --> 00:41:43,340
Pregnant?

437
00:41:43,340 --> 00:41:46,560
Your Mighty Monarch, the Heavenly Tribe has always placed great importance in law.

438
00:41:46,560 --> 00:41:51,030
For them to lock up a pregnant mortal in the Heavenly Palace,

439
00:41:51,030 --> 00:41:55,420
this situation is definitely not that simple.

440
00:41:56,460 --> 00:42:01,600
I'm here in the Heavenly Palace this time to plead for my sin.

441
00:42:02,490 --> 00:42:07,270
I cannot help anybody else.

442
00:42:42,330 --> 00:42:46,390
”Cold” by Aska Yang & Diamond Zhang

